
Response Formats

路 PDF: For printing and signatures
路 DOCX: For editing in word processors
路 HTML: For web display
路 JSON: For data exchange

3. Compliance API

Compliance Check Endpoint

```http
POST /api/compliance/check
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "grantData": { ... },
  "jurisdiction": "US_FEDERAL",
  "grantType": "discretionary",
  "checkTypes": ["financial", "programmatic", "administrative"]
}

Response:
{
  "compliant": true,
  "warnings": [],
  "requirements": [
    {
      "id": "2CFR200.300",
      "description": "Financial management system requirements",
      "status": "compliant",
      "evidence": "system_audit_report_2024.pdf"
    }
  ]
}
